<body>
<segment id="1" parent="1001" relname="preparation">Run a Sweepstakes</segment>
<segment id="2" parent="1002" relname="span">A sweepstakes can really help your ' bottom line ' ,</segment>
<segment id="3" parent="2" relname="means">by adding to your mailing list and your contacts .</segment>
<segment id="4" parent="1004" relname="span">Read this article</segment>
<segment id="5" parent="6" relname="attribution">to learn</segment>
<segment id="6" parent="1005" relname="span">how to do one properly .</segment>
<segment id="7" parent="1008" relname="preparation">Steps</segment>
<segment id="8" parent="1009" relname="span">Have the infrastructure</segment>
<segment id="9" parent="8" relname="purpose">to support it .</segment>
<segment id="10" parent="1011" relname="span">You will need to have a server</segment>
<segment id="11" parent="10" relname="elaboration">that can handle the load .</segment>
<segment id="12" parent="1013" relname="span">The world is full of people</segment>
<segment id="13" parent="1014" relname="joint">who want something for nothing</segment>
<segment id="14" parent="1014" relname="joint">and a lot of those people invest a lot of time in it !</segment>
<segment id="15" parent="1016" relname="preparation">Infrastructure would be :</segment>
<segment id="16" parent="1017" relname="preparation">Server</segment>
<segment id="17" parent="1018" relname="preparation">Mail list support</segment>
<segment id="18" parent="1019" relname="span">Database support</segment>
<segment id="19" parent="1020" relname="span">( for the information</segment>
<segment id="20" parent="1021" relname="span">received</segment>
<segment id="21" parent="20" relname="circumstance">when they fill out entries )</segment>
<segment id="22" parent="1024" relname="span">Do some research into various organizations</segment>
<segment id="23" parent="22" relname="elaboration">that do data collection .</segment>
<segment id="24" parent="1025" relname="span">Learning , and utilizing , the demographics is one of the many uses of data</segment>
<segment id="25" parent="24" relname="elaboration">received in a sweepstakes .</segment>
<segment id="26" parent="1027" relname="same_unit">Be sure the one</segment>
<segment id="27" parent="28" relname="attribution">you get</segment>
<segment id="28" parent="1028" relname="span">will work for you .</segment>
<segment id="29" parent="1030" relname="same_unit">Understand that</segment>
<segment id="30" parent="31" relname="circumstance">when you offer prizes ,</segment>
<segment id="31" parent="1032" relname="span">( usually offered by a third party ) ,</segment>
<segment id="32" parent="1033" relname="span">that you may be limited</segment>
<segment id="33" parent="32" relname="manner">as to who can enter .</segment>
<segment id="34" parent="1034" relname="sequence">Be prepared for the fallout from the rest of the world !</segment>
<segment id="35" parent="1036" relname="span">Understand , and accept ,</segment>
<segment id="36" parent="35" relname="elaboration">that it will never be easy enough .</segment>
<segment id="37" parent="1038" relname="span">Some people just wo n't get it .</segment>
<segment id="38" parent="1039" relname="span">Be prepared to either have a bunch of FAQs for every problem</segment>
<segment id="39" parent="1040" relname="contrast">they have ,</segment>
<segment id="40" parent="1040" relname="contrast">or ready to answer all of their emails .</segment>
<segment id="41" parent="1042" relname="span">Do n't have there be just one method</segment>
<segment id="42" parent="41" relname="elaboration">of entering it .</segment>
<segment id="43" parent="1044" relname="span">Some methods</segment>
<segment id="44" parent="43" relname="elaboration">that you can use are :</segment>
<segment id="45" parent="1046" relname="preparation">Form entry</segment>
<segment id="46" parent="1046" relname="span">A hard-coded link to the form</segment>
<segment id="47" parent="1047" relname="sequence">Have a way for them to enter manually ,</segment>
<segment id="48" parent="1049" relname="preparation">as in the terms and conditions</segment>
<segment id="49" parent="1049" relname="sequence">Understand what compliance is</segment>
<segment id="50" parent="1051" relname="sequence">and how it varies from state to state .</segment>
<segment id="51" parent="1051" relname="sequence">And then Be Compliant .</segment>
<segment id="52" parent="1054" relname="span">One things</segment>
<segment id="53" parent="52" relname="elaboration">you can do</segment>
<segment id="54" parent="1055" relname="joint">is ' borrow ' the terms and conditions from a similar contest</segment>
<segment id="55" parent="1055" relname="joint">and adopt it to your purposes .</segment>
<segment id="56" parent="1058" relname="attribution">Know</segment>
<segment id="57" parent="1058" relname="span">that your email list will not be exactly the goldmine</segment>
<segment id="58" parent="57" relname="elaboration">you are expecting .</segment>
<segment id="59" parent="60" relname="condition">When you start sending out emails ,</segment>
<segment id="60" parent="1060" relname="span">you will get many unsubscribe requests .</segment>
<segment id="61" parent="1062" relname="span">Especially ,</segment>
<segment id="62" parent="61" relname="condition">if it gets picked up by a sweepstake offering site .</segment>
<segment id="63" parent="1064" relname="contrast">You will come out ahead ,</segment>
<segment id="64" parent="1064" relname="contrast">but be prepared to be narrowing it down for a while .</segment>
<segment id="65" parent="1065" relname="sequence">Make sure your selection will be random .</segment>
<segment id="66" parent="1067" relname="span">There are sites online</segment>
<segment id="67" parent="66" relname="elaboration">that will generate a random number for you .</segment>
<segment id="68" parent="1069" relname="span">Each entry will have a number ,</segment>
<segment id="69" parent="68" relname="result">so choose a random number from there .</segment>
<segment id="70" parent="1070" relname="span">Be able to manage the costs .</segment>
<segment id="71" parent="1071" relname="span">The costs will come from the infrastructure</segment>
<segment id="72" parent="1072" relname="span">mentioned before as well as other costs</segment>
<segment id="73" parent="72" relname="elaboration">you might incur .</segment>
<segment id="74" parent="1074" relname="preparation">Tips</segment>
<segment id="75" parent="1074" relname="joint">Most companies pass off the tax liability to the winners .</segment>
<segment id="76" parent="1076" relname="contrast">Be sure they understand ,</segment>
<segment id="77" parent="1077" relname="span">or the opportunity is there for them ,</segment>
<segment id="78" parent="1078" relname="span">that</segment>
<segment id="79" parent="78" relname="circumstance">when entering your contest .</segment>
<segment id="80" parent="81" relname="condition">If you are not incorporated ,</segment>
<segment id="81" parent="1081" relname="span">it is not a good idea to hold a sweepstakes .</segment>
<segment id="82" parent="1080" relname="span">You will be opening yourself to lawsuits .</segment>
<segment id="83" parent="1082" relname="span">Contact your local tax authority</segment>
<segment id="84" parent="1083" relname="span">so that they can tell you how to deal with the value of the prize</segment>
<segment id="85" parent="84" relname="elaboration">being offered .</segment>
